Minecraft yǐ hàu-jìn nèi-tsuén.

telemetry.event.performance_metrics.desc:
Liǎu-jiě Minecraft de jěng-tǐ shìng-néng gài-kuàng, kě-yǐ bāng-jù wǒ-men jēn-duèi gè-jǔng jī-shíng hé tsāu-tzuò-shì-tǔng tiáu-jěng yǔ yōu-huà yóu-shì. 
Yóu-shì bǎn-běn-shìn-shī yě bāu-hán tzài chí-jūng, yǐ bāng-jù wǒ-men bǐ-jiàu Minecraft shīn bǎn-běn de shìng-néng gài-kuàng.

telemetry.event.world_load_times.title: Shr̀-jiè jiā-tzài shŕ-jiān
telemetry.event.world_loaded.description:
Liǎu-jiě wán-jiā wán Minecraft shŕ de shì-jié (lì-rú yóu-shì mó-shr̀、kè-hù-duān huò fú-wù-duān shr̀-fǒu bèi shiū-gǎi, yǐ-jí yóu-shì bǎn-běn) yǒu-jù-yú wǒ-men tzài yóu-shì gēng-shīn shŕ jù-jung gǎi-jìn wán-jiā tzuèi guān-shīn de bù-fen. 
Shr̀-jiè jiā-tzài shr̀-jiàn jiāng túng shr̀-jiè shiè-tzài shr̀-jiàn yī-chǐ yung4-yú jì-suàn yóu-shì huèi-huà de chŕ-shù shŕ jǎng.
